**************
pyticketswitch
**************

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pyticketswitch.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyticketswitch

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/ingresso-group/pyticketswitch.svg?branch=master
